<p>Reggie is now legally blind after being diagnosed with a degenerative eye condition called retinitis pigmentosa.</p>

<p>She has lost 90 per cent of her vision and walks with the aid of a cane.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, her son suffers from cystic fibrosis, an inherited disorder that causes severe damage to the lungs, digestive system and other organs in the body.</p>

